## Limitations

This report is based on available data and sources up to October 2023. The analysis may not fully capture the most recent shifts in voter behavior or emerging trends within the Republican Party. Additionally, the perspectives included are primarily from English-language sources, which may not represent the full spectrum of opinions and motivations among Republican voters.